-- Otokar Falls in Istanbul After First-Quarter Profit Declines
-- B y   S i b e l   A k b a y
-- 2012-05-03T15:19:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-03/otokar-falls-in-istanbul-after-first-quarter-profit-declines-1-.html
Otokar Otomotiv & Savunma Sanayi AS (OTKAR) , a
Turkish producer of buses and military trucks, fell after
reporting that first-quarter profit declined 31 percent.  Otokar dropped 2.3 percent to 30.2 liras at the close in
Istanbul, the lowest level in more than a week. Net income fell
to 6.33 million liras ($3.6 million) from 9.19 million liras in
the first quarter of 2011, Otokar said in a statement to the
 Istanbul Stock Exchange  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sibel Akbay in Istanbul at 
